recipe.label: Sparkling Cranberries
ingredientLines: More sugar for coating: i do a mix of medium-grained organic sugar for the first coating, and then a second toss with regular granulated white sugar. you don't want a huge grain for that first toss, just something larger than standard sugar, smaller than most turbinado sugars. you can sort of see the different grain sizes in the third photo in the main write-up.
